@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityDiamondFontSize 11
skinparam ActivityFontSize 11
skinparam partitionBorderColor #333333
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #555555

|User|
start
:Click "Export to PDF";

|Frontend|
if (Has calculation?) then (yes)
  :Show loading indicator;
  :Generate PDF from state;
  
  note right
    **Pure Frontend Operation**
    No backend API call
    
    **PDF Contents:**
    - Summary & header
    - Container info
    - Utilization stats
    - Items breakdown
    - Unfitted items (if any)
    - Step-by-step pages with
      2D schematics (top/front/side)
  end note
  
  :Trigger browser download;
  :Show success message;
  
else (no)
  :Show "Calculate first" error;
endif

|User|
:View result;
stop

@enduml
